-When you start the "bibliotheca" application, you will see the main menu:

Welcome to The Bangalore Public Library System - Bibliotheca !
PLEASE TYPE THE INDEX OF THE OPTION IN THE MENU :
1. View all books
2. Reserve a book
3. Check library number

-Then you type number below + Enter, you will see different information looks like:

...
(You can type 'exit' to quit or any other words to continue...)

-Then if type "exit", you'll close the application; otherwise, go back to the main menu.

-Others are as the same with requirement.


